targets.query:
from(bucket: "mina-benchmarks")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["category"] =~ /^mina-base$/)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] =~ /^${fieldFilterQuery:regex}$/)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] =~ /^${measurementFilterQuery:regex}$/)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["gitbranch"] =~ /^${gitbranchFilterQuery:regex}$/)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["gitbranch"] =~ /^${gitbranchFilterQuery:regex}$/)
  //|> group(columns: ["_measurement"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
